sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main
    participant G as Game
    participant S as Snake
    participant F as Food
    participant Sc as Score
    M->>G: create game
    G->>S: create snake
    G->>F: create food
    G->>Sc: create score
    loop Game Loop
        G->>S: move snake
        S->>S: check collision
        alt collision detected
            G->>G: end game
        else no collision
            S->>F: eat food
            alt food eaten
                Sc->>Sc: increment score
                F->>F: generate new food
            end
        end
    end
